OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and sunny start, but
OL,6,Fcloud will tend to increase from the
OL,7,Fnorth throughout the day, with a
OL,8,Fscattering of showers developing.
OL,9,FShowers potentially turning heavier
OL,10,Finto the afternoon. Feeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRather cloudy overnight with
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain slowly
OL,14,Fclearing southwards during the night.
OL,15,FRather breezy, particularly near
OL,16,FBristol Channel coasts. Turning chilly
OL,17,Fin the north under clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
